	<h1 class="title">这个智能手表要通过你，来感知触摸到的物体</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3910/small/3910.png?1418028195" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐怡园 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-11 06:05:42 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17353/medium/17353.jpg?1447145758" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


